name: Baby Delivery
description:
I made this today in a couple of hours as homework for my Bradley Method birthing class. It happened to go great with the theme of "I want to be free" since you end up birthing a baby by the end! And what's a more wholesome interpretation of the theme than that. 

All art, music, and code was written by me in the last 5 or 6 hours using Gamemaker Studio 2.

Alarm and Button Press SFX - https://opengameart.org/content/512-sound-effects-8-bit-style
